{"tid":2323452,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一個post話你知點解幾億人打唔贏日本仔（多曱甴圖慎入）","createTime":"2020-12-13T07:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T08:24:17.000Z","uid":259980,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d387d02752550172fed129bb8dc9a19a7960898","tid":2323452,"uid":259980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">原因一：支那人<br />\n走啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n槍啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FU2YFOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFU2YFOw.png&h=4a06ec61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">原因二：下下講幾億人，無事做下奴工就有咁多人。有事要打仗，二百人都唔知有無。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0jUXbVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0jUXbVb.png&h=97681e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">原因三：因為出嚟同日本人打嘅都係on9仔，腦充血。中國人就識明哲保身。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T5h55fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT5h55fc.png&h=84764dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">原因四：中國人奴性強，服從日本人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7FZ9GS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7FZ9GS.png&h=420dc044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">原因七：中國人同情日本仔，怕佢地受傷，會失國際支持</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jt1DAd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jt1DAd.png&h=8b2a3f34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">原因八：因為中國人係羊，日本人係牧羊犬，羊求遠會驚牧羊犬</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G7bFT8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG7bFT8y.png&h=1ac0e5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">結論：中國會輸，其實係因為班放負撚係咁講中國人唔團結又懦弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你成班社運垃圾剩係識放負<br />\n你地同鄭蟲泰之流其實無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真正香港人只會當你地係曱甴仔=藍絲<br />\n無人當過你地手跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />898<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"6027a77329f31614a1f03ac9b56a1d9d37ec7cfb","tid":2323452,"uid":259980,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"入面仲有好多曱甴仔歡迎入去block<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為甚麼中國十三人億會攻不下一個小小的台灣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2323426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2323426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bbfd828ddfb1cb6c408c7a11e5ae104c8ed4eef6","tid":2323452,"uid":259980,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"幫大家block返幾隻曱甴<br />\n維護連登清淨人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj